09:22.729 --> 09:24.064
Oh god.

09:24.314 --> 09:26.775
- Hello, Magda. -Hey.

09:26.941 --> 09:28.401
- How are you? -Good.

09:28.651 --> 09:30.028
My kitty.

09:31.154 --> 09:34.157
We have to go. Get ready, honey.

09:36.368 --> 09:39.829
