09:39.996 --> 09:44.125
On Sunday? You should have called me instead of the babysitter.

09:44.376 --> 09:47.128
As if you weren't going to order Magda.

09:47.295 --> 09:49.339
- Not on weekends. -Sure, of course.

09:49.589 --> 09:52.550
