18:15.261 --> 18:16.763
Hey ...

18:17.681 --> 18:19.683
Are you sleeping?

18:19.933 --> 18:22.644
I just want to watch TV.

18:22.811 --> 18:25.146
Hm ... don't eat anything?

18:25.313 --> 18:28.900
- I don't like broccoli. -You don’t like broccoli.

18:29.609 --> 18:32.445
- I can make you some pasta. -No.

18:32.612 --> 18:34.114
Okay.

18:35.323 --> 18:36.825
All right.

18:37.075 --> 18:39.869
- She is a touch warm. - Yes, she was coughing a bit.

18:40.036 --> 18:42.205
I hope it's not flu.

18:42.372 --> 18:44.124
- Okay thanks. -Okay, bye.

18:44.290 --> 18:46.876
- Bye, bye.

19:17.574 --> 19:19.409
Love of my life.

19:24.581 --> 19:26.666
Thanks for coming by.

19:30.086 --> 19:33.631
I feel terrible and Zoe is sick now.

19:33.798 --> 19:35.175
What a day.

19:35.425 --> 19:38.636
But now you are done, with that agreement.

19:38.803 --> 19:43.099
Sure.
Then every time we disagree on a vacation plant we can go to court.

19:45.643 --> 19:47.437
You know...

19:47.604 --> 19:50.482
Yesterday when we were together in the zoo

19:51.441 --> 19:54.361
It was like we were a family.

19:58.531 --> 20:02.243
I never felt that with James, it was never happy.

20:02.410 --> 20:05.163
He never trusted me as a mother

20:05.330 --> 20:07.957
