23:52.599 --> 23:54.142
- Please meet me there. -OK.

23:54.392 --> 23:56.811
Any block to the head yesterday?

23:56.978 --> 23:59.564
- No, I don't know, I wasn't with her all day!
-Was she feeling sick last night?

23:59.814 --> 24:02.442
